# Build artifacts, untracked as of v1.1.92. These are generated by `tsc`/`vite`
# on every build and were previously committed, so each build produced a dirty
# tree and every real change arrived buried in incidental churn. Nothing in the
# repo imports vite.config.js (the .ts is the source the Vite CLI loads); the
# .tsbuildinfo pair are incremental-compile caches.
